    "translation":{"eng":"(You will develop deep attachment to kṛṣṇa-nāma.) (Then) auto­matically your life will become successful. (Without attachment to Śrī Kṛṣṇa, this life is simply useless.) (If you receive the mercy of Śrī Gaurāṅga,) (ultimately) you will receive the darśana of Śrī Śrī Rādhā-Śyāmasundara in Vṛndāvana."}}
